  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Beyond the conference</span>
    <h1>Network events</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">
      Online and hybrid events organised by EISS, the COST Action <a href="https://netsec-cost.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NetSec</a>, and partner institutions. All events are free and open to anyone working in or alongside European security studies. No membership required.
    </p>
